OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1777975605
OL,3,CBarnet Council to receive additional
OL,4,C#500,000 funding after antisemitic
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThe government will provide an
OL,8,Fadditional #500,000 to Barnet Council
OL,9,Ffollowing a spate of antisemitic
OL,10,Fattacks in the area.
OL,12,FThe funding comes in addition to an
OL,13,Fextra #1 million of funding for Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunities across England.
OL,16,FThe money is expected to pay for
OL,17,Fcommunity safety work and projects
OL,18,Faimed at countering antisemitic
OL,19,Fnarratives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
