OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1777975605
OL,3,CBarnet Council to receive additional
OL,4,C#500,000 funding after antisemitic
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThe announcement comes as Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer prepares to host senior
OL,9,Ffigures from public life in Downing
OL,10,FStreet to discuss a "whole of society"
OL,11,Fresponse to antisemitism in the wake
OL,12,Fof the stabbing of two Jewish men in
OL,13,FGolders Green last week.
OL,15,FThe Prime Minister will warn everyone
OL,16,Fhas a responsibility to stand with
OL,17,FJewish communities as attacks on
OL,18,FBritish Jews are "a crisis for all of
OL,19,Fus" and "a test of our values".
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@fO]zD@ROU{D@CO]{D@IOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1777975605
OL,3,CBarnet Council to receive additional
OL,4,C#500,000 funding after antisemitic
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FTuesday's meetings are expected to
OL,8,Finclude senior ministers and police
OL,9,Fchiefs, along with representatives
OL,10,Ffrom the arts, higher education, trade
OL,11,Funions and businesses including the
OL,12,FCBI.
OL,14,FSir Keir will later focus on the
OL,15,Fdomestic security implications of the
OL,16,FIran war, including a heightened
OL,17,Fthreat to Jewish communities, during a
OL,18,Fministerial meeting of the Middle East
OL,19,FResponse Committee, the crisis team
OL,20,Fset up to respond to conflict.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
