FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1777975605
OL,3,CBarnet Council to receive additional
OL,4,C#500,000 funding after antisemitic
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,8,F"While we know there is more to do, we
OL,9,Fbelieve that quickly channelling
OL,10,Fgovernment funding directly to the
OL,11,Fcommunities and places facing the
OL,12,Fgreatest risks today will help local
OL,13,Fpartners to take early, practical
OL,14,Faction to keep people safe, strengthen
OL,15,Fcommunities and stand up to hate.".
OL,17,FThe funding follows the #25 million
OL,18,Fannounced last week in response to the
OL,19,Fattack in Golders Green to provide
OL,20,Fmore security for Jewish communities.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
